#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:275
msgid "Your Mortgage Results"
msgstr "住宅ローンの結果"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:276
msgid ""
"Enter your loan details and click Calculate to see your monthly payment "
"breakdown."
msgstr "ローンの詳細を入力し、「計算」をクリックすると、毎月の支払いの内訳が表示されます。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:351
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:165
msgid "in interest and pay off"
msgstr "利息を払って返済する"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:421
msgid "The total purchase price of the home"
msgstr "住宅の購入価格の総額"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:425
#, python-format
msgid "Your upfront payment (20%% avoids PMI)"
msgstr "前払い（20%% が PMI を回避）"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:429
msgid "Choose Loan Term"
msgstr "融資期間を選択してください"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:429
msgid "15 or 30 years are most common"
msgstr "15年または30年が最も一般的です"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:433
msgid "Enter Interest Rate"
msgstr "金利を入力してください"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:433
msgid "Your loan's annual percentage rate"
msgstr "ローンの年率"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:437
msgid "Add Taxes & Insurance"
msgstr "税金と保険を追加する"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:437
msgid "Optional but gives accurate PITI payment"
msgstr "オプションですが、正確な PITI 支払いを提供します"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:448
msgid "Understanding Your Payment (PITI)"
msgstr "お支払いについて（PITI）"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:453
msgid "The amount that goes toward paying off your loan balance"
msgstr "ローン残高の返済に充てられる金額"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:457
msgid "The cost of borrowing money from the lender"
msgstr "貸し手からお金を借りる際のコスト"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:461
msgid "Property taxes paid to local government"
msgstr "地方自治体に支払われる固定資産税"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:465
msgid "Homeowners insurance protects your investment"
msgstr "住宅所有者保険があなたの投資を保護します"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:482
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Private Mortgage Insurance (PMI) is typically required when your down "
"payment is less than 20%%. It protects the lender if you default and usually"
" costs 0.3%% to 1.5%% of the loan annually."
msgstr ""
"通常、頭金が 20%% 未満の場合は、プライベート住宅ローン保険 (PMI) が必要です。債務不履行の場合に貸し手を保護し、通常は年間ローンの "
"0.3%% ～ 1.5%% の費用がかかります。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:485
msgid "Should I choose a 15-year or 30-year mortgage?"
msgstr "住宅ローンは15年と30年のどちらを選択すべきでしょうか?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:486
msgid ""
"A 15-year mortgage has higher monthly payments but lower total interest. A "
"30-year mortgage has lower monthly payments but you pay more interest over "
"time. Choose based on your budget and goals."
msgstr ""
"15 年の住宅ローンでは月々の支払額は高くなりますが、総利息は低くなります。 30 "
"年の住宅ローンでは月々の支払額は減りますが、長期的に支払う利息は増加します。予算や目的に応じてお選びください。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:489
msgid "How much should I put down on a house?"
msgstr "家にいくら頭金を付けるべきでしょうか？"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:490
#, python-format
msgid ""
"20%% is ideal to avoid PMI, but many loans allow 3-5%% down. A larger down "
"payment means lower monthly payments and less interest paid overall."
msgstr ""
"PMIを回避するには20%%が理想的ですが、多くのローンは3〜5%%の低下を許容します。頭金が大きいほど、月々の支払額が減り、支払われる利息全体が少なくなります。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:493
msgid "How can extra payments save me money?"
msgstr "追加料金を支払うとどのように節約できますか?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:494
msgid ""
"Extra payments go directly toward principal, reducing your balance faster. "
"This means you pay less interest over the life of the loan and can pay off "
"your mortgage years earlier."
msgstr ""
"追加の支払いは元本に直接当てられるため、残高がより早く減ります。これは、ローン期間全体にわたって支払う利息が減り、何年も早く住宅ローンを完済できることを意味します。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:509
msgid "Improve Your Credit Score"
msgstr "信用スコアを向上させる"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:510
msgid ""
"A higher credit score can qualify you for lower interest rates, saving "
"thousands over the loan term."
msgstr "信用スコアが高いほど低金利での利用が可能となり、ローン期間にわたって数千円を節約できます。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:513
msgid "Make Biweekly Payments"
msgstr "隔週で支払いを行う"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:514
msgid ""
"Pay half your monthly payment every two weeks. You'll make 13 full payments "
"per year instead of 12."
msgstr "毎月の支払いの半分を 2 週間ごとに支払います。年間 12 回ではなく 13 回の全額支払いを行うことになります。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:517
msgid "Shop Multiple Lenders"
msgstr "複数の貸し手を利用する"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:518
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Get quotes from at least 3 lenders. Even a 0.25%% rate difference can save "
"thousands."
msgstr "少なくとも3社の金融業者から見積もりを取得してください。 0.25%% のレートの違いでも、数千ドルの節約が可能です。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/mortgage_calculator.html:549
msgid "Affordability"
msgstr "手頃な価格"

