msgid "Choose Term"
msgstr "期間の選択"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:281
msgid ""
"Select your repayment term - shorter terms mean higher payments but less "
"interest."
msgstr "返済期間を選択してください。返済期間が短いと支払額は高くなりますが、利息は少なくなります。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:287
msgid "Compare Plans"
msgstr "プランを比較する"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:288
msgid ""
"See how different plans and extra payments affect your payoff timeline."
msgstr "さまざまなプランや追加支払いが支払いスケジュールにどのような影響を与えるかを確認してください。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:300
msgid "What repayment plan should I choose?"
msgstr "どのような返済プランを選べばよいのでしょうか？"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:306
msgid ""
"Standard 10-year is best if you can afford it - you'll pay the least "
"interest. If payments are too high, consider income-driven plans or extended"
" repayment. Always pay as much as you can afford."
msgstr ""
"余裕がある場合は標準 10 "
"年が最適です。支払う利息が最小限になります。支払いが高すぎる場合は、収入に応じた計画や返済の延長を検討してください。常に余裕のある額を支払います。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:318
msgid ""
"Extra payments go directly to principal, reducing the balance faster. This "
"means less interest over time and earlier payoff. Even $50/month extra can "
"save thousands and years on your loan."
msgstr ""
"追加の支払いは元本に直接支払われるため、残高がより早く減ります。これは、時間の経過とともに利息が減り、早期に返済できることを意味します。月額 50 "
"ドルの追加でも、ローンを何千年も節約できます。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:324
msgid "What about loan forgiveness?"
msgstr "ローン免除についてはどうですか？"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:330
msgid ""
"Public Service Loan Forgiveness (PSLF) forgives remaining balance after 120 "
"qualifying payments while working for government/nonprofit. Income-driven "
"plans forgive after 20-25 years. Forgiven amounts may be taxable."
msgstr ""
"公共サービスローン免除 (PSLF) は、政府/非営利団体で働いている間、対象となる 120 回の支払い後の残りの残高を免除します。収入重視のプランは "
"20 ～ 25 年後に許容されます。免除された金額は課税対象となる場合があります。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:336
msgid "Should I refinance my student loans?"
msgstr "学生ローンを借り換えるべきでしょうか?"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:342
msgid ""
"Refinancing can lower your rate if you have good credit and stable income. "
"However, refinancing federal loans means losing benefits like income-driven "
"plans and forgiveness options. Only refinance if you don't need these "
"protections."
msgstr ""
"良好な信用と安定した収入がある場合、借り換えは金利を下げることができます。ただし、連邦融資の借り換えは、収入に応じたプランや免除オプションなどの特典を失うことを意味します。これらの保護が必要ない場合にのみ借り換えてください。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:350
msgid "Student Loan Tips"
msgstr "学生ローンのヒント"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:356
#, python-format
msgid "Set up autopay - most servicers offer a 0.25%% rate reduction."
msgstr "自動支払いを設定します - ほとんどのサービサーは 0.25%% の料金割引を提供しています。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:362
msgid ""
"Pay highest interest loans first (avalanche method) to minimize interest."
msgstr "利息を最小限に抑えるために、最も利息の高いローンを最初に支払います (雪崩方式)。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:368
msgid ""
"Make payments during grace period to reduce principal before interest "
"accrues."
msgstr "猶予期間中に支払いを行うと、利息が発生する前に元本が減ります。"

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/student_loan_calculator.html:374
msgid ""
"Check for employer student loan assistance - it's an increasingly common "
"benefit."
msgstr "雇用主の学生ローン補助を確認してください。これはますます一般的な給付金です。"

