#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:396
msgid "What are Calories?"
msgstr "カロリーとは何ですか?"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:398
msgid ""
"A calorie is a unit of energy. In nutrition, calories refer to the energy "
"people get from the food and drink they consume, and the energy they use in "
"physical activity. The number of calories you need each day depends on your "
"age, gender, height, weight, and activity level."
msgstr ""
"カロリーはエネルギーの単位です。栄養学において、カロリーとは、人々が消費する食べ物や飲み物から得られるエネルギー、および身体活動で使用されるエネルギーを指します。毎日必要なカロリー数は、年齢、性別、身長、体重、活動レベルによって異なります。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:401
msgid ""
"Understanding your daily calorie needs is essential for achieving your "
"fitness goals, whether you want to lose weight, maintain your current "
"weight, or gain muscle."
msgstr ""
"体重を減らしたい、現在の体重を維持したい、筋肉を増やしたいなどのフィットネス目標を達成するには、毎日のカロリー必要量を理解することが不可欠です。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:407
msgid "Understanding BMR and TDEE"
msgstr "BMR と TDEE を理解する"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:412
msgid ""
"The number of calories your body burns at rest to maintain basic life "
"functions like breathing, circulation, and cell production."
msgstr "呼吸、循環、細胞生成などの基本的な生活機能を維持するために安静時に体が燃焼するカロリーの数。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:418
msgid ""
"Your total daily calorie burn, including BMR plus calories burned through "
"physical activity and exercise. This is the number of calories you need to "
"maintain your current weight."
msgstr "BMR と身体活動や運動による消費カロリーを含む、1 日の総消費カロリー。これは、現在の体重を維持するために必要なカロリー数です。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:422
msgid "Target Calories"
msgstr "目標カロリー"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:424
msgid ""
"Your TDEE adjusted based on your goal. A deficit (negative adjustment) helps"
" you lose weight, while a surplus (positive adjustment) helps you gain "
"weight."
msgstr ""
"TDEE は目標に基づいて調整されます。不足（マイナスの調整）は体重を減らすのに役立ちますが、過剰（プラスの調整）は体重を増やすのに役立ちます。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:432
msgid "Calorie Goals Explained"
msgstr "カロリー目標の説明"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:434
msgid "Lose Weight Fast (-1000 cal):"
msgstr "早く体重を減らす (-1000 cal):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:434
msgid ""
"Aggressive weight loss. May be difficult to maintain long-term. Consult a "
"healthcare provider."
msgstr "積極的な減量。長期的に維持するのは難しいかもしれません。医療提供者に相談してください。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:435
msgid "Lose Weight (-500 cal):"
msgstr "体重を減らす (-500 カロリー):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:435
msgid ""
"Moderate weight loss. Typically results in ~0.5 kg (1 lb) per week. "
"Sustainable for most people."
msgstr "中程度の体重減少。通常、1 週間あたり約 0.5 kg (1 ポンド) になります。ほとんどの人にとって持続可能です。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:436
msgid "Lose Weight Slowly (-250 cal):"
msgstr "ゆっくりと体重を減らす (-250 カロリー):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:436
msgid ""
"Gradual weight loss. Typically results in ~0.25 kg (0.5 lb) per week. Very "
"sustainable."
msgstr "徐々に体重が減少します。通常、1 週間あたり約 0.25 kg (0.5 ポンド) になります。非常に持続可能です。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:437
msgid "Maintain Weight (0 cal):"
msgstr "体重を維持します (0 カロリー):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:437
msgid "Eat at your TDEE level to maintain your current weight."
msgstr "現在の体重を維持するには、TDEE レベルで食事をしましょう。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:438
msgid "Gain Weight Slowly (+250 cal):"
msgstr "ゆっくりと体重を増やす (+250 カロリー):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:438
msgid "Gradual weight gain. Good for lean muscle building."
msgstr "徐々に体重が増加。引き締まった筋肉の構築に適しています。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:439
msgid "Gain Weight (+500 cal):"
msgstr "体重増加 (+500 カロリー):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:439
msgid "Moderate weight gain. Typically results in ~0.5 kg (1 lb) per week."
msgstr "適度な体重増加。通常、1 週間あたり約 0.5 kg (1 ポンド) になります。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:440
msgid "Gain Weight Fast (+1000 cal):"
msgstr "体重を早く増やす (+1000 cal):"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:440
msgid "Aggressive weight gain. May result in more fat gain than muscle."
msgstr "激しい体重増加。筋肉よりも脂肪が多くなる可能性があります。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:446
msgid "Understanding Macronutrients"
msgstr "主要栄養素を理解する"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:449
msgid "Protein (4 calories per gram)"
msgstr "タンパク質（1グラムあたり4カロリー）"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:451
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Essential for muscle repair and growth. Higher protein intake is recommended"
" for weight loss (35%%) and muscle gain (30%%)."
msgstr "筋肉の修復と成長に不可欠です。体重減少 (35%%) と筋肉増加 (30%%) のためには、タンパク質の摂取量を増やすことが推奨されます。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:455
msgid "Carbohydrates (4 calories per gram)"
msgstr "炭水化物（1グラムあたり4カロリー）"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:457
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Primary energy source. Higher carb intake (45%%) is recommended for weight "
"gain, moderate (35-40%%) for maintenance and weight loss."
msgstr "一次エネルギー源。体重増加には炭水化物の摂取量を多く（45%%）、維持と減量には適度（35～40%%）を推奨します。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:461
msgid "Fat (9 calories per gram)"
msgstr "脂肪（1グラムあたり9カロリー）"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:463
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Important for hormone production and nutrient absorption. Typically 25-30%% "
"of total calories."
msgstr "ホルモンの生成と栄養素の吸収に重要です。通常、総カロリーの 25 ～ 30%%。"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:476
msgid "Choose your fitness goal (lose weight, maintain, or gain weight)"
msgstr "フィットネスの目標を選択します (体重を減らす、維持する、または増やす)"

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/calorie_calculator.html:477
