msgid ""
"The calculated area of your shape in square units. This is the primary "
"result showing how much space the shape covers."
msgstr "正方形単位で計算されたシェイプの面積。これは、形状がカバーするスペースの量を示す主な結果です。"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:466
msgid "Perimeter/Circumference"
msgstr "外周/円周"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:468
msgid ""
"The total distance around the shape. For circles, this is called "
"circumference. For polygons, it's the sum of all side lengths."
msgstr "シェイプの周囲の合計距離。円の場合、これは円周と呼ばれます。ポリゴンの場合、すべての辺の長さの合計です。"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:474
msgid ""
"A detailed breakdown of how the area was calculated, showing each step of "
"the formula application."
msgstr "面積の計算方法の詳細な内訳。数式適用の各ステップが示されています。"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:478
msgid "Charts & Visualizations"
msgstr "チャートとビジュアライゼーション"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:480
msgid ""
"Visual representations of your calculation including area gauge, properties "
"comparison, and shape measurements."
msgstr "面積ゲージ、特性比較、形状測定などの計算を視覚的に表現します。"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:494
msgid ""
"All measurements must be in the same unit. The calculator will display "
"results in square units (e.g., m², cm², in²)."
msgstr "すべての測定値は同じ単位である必要があります。計算機は結果を平方単位 (m²、cm²、in² など) で表示します。"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:500
msgid ""
"For regular polygons (pentagon, hexagon, octagon), all sides must be equal "
"length."
msgstr "正多角形（五角形、六角形、八角形）の場合、すべての辺が同じ長さでなければなりません。"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:506
msgid ""
"Calculations use high-precision mathematics (SymPy) for accurate results, "
"especially for circular shapes."
msgstr "計算には高精度数学 (SymPy) が使用され、特に円形の場合に正確な結果が得られます。"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:512
#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/circle_calculator.html:407
msgid ""
"Results are rounded to 8 decimal places for display, but calculations use "
"full precision internally."
msgstr "結果は表示のために小数点以下 8 桁に四捨五入されますが、計算では内部的に完全な精度が使用されます。"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/area_calculator.html:519
