msgstr "選択したベースに数字を入力してください"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:487
msgid "Click 'Calculate' to see results in all number bases"
msgstr "「計算」をクリックすると、すべての基数での結果が表示されます。"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:488
msgid "View bit comparison charts and step-by-step solutions"
msgstr "ビット比較チャートと段階的な解決策を表示する"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:496
msgid "Binary arithmetic: Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, Division"
msgstr "二項演算: 加算、減算、乗算、除算"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:497
msgid "Bitwise operations: AND, OR, XOR, NAND, NOR, NOT"
msgstr "ビット演算: AND、OR、XOR、NAND、NOR、NOT"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:498
msgid "Bit shifts: Left shift (<<), Right shift (>>)"
msgstr "ビットシフト: 左シフト (<<)、右シフト (>>)"

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/binary_calculator.html:499
