msgstr "「コースを追加」ボタンをクリックしてコースを追加します。"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gpa_calculator.html:228
msgid ""
"Enter the course name, select the grade, and enter the number of credits for"
" each course."
msgstr "コース名を入力し、学年を選択し、各コースの単位数を入力します。"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gpa_calculator.html:229
msgid ""
"Optionally, enter your current GPA and credits earned to calculate "
