"Convert between hours, minutes, seconds, and days. Supports all common time "
"unit conversions with precise calculations."
msgstr "時間、分、秒、日の間で変換します。正確な計算によるすべての一般的な時間単位変換をサポートします。"

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/hours_calculator.html:314
